406,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/03\/umar-fear-allah-civilians\/","url_meta":{"origin":6637,"position":1},"title":"Umar on War: Fear Allah regarding non-combatants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 3, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Wahb reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, decreed, \u201cDo not steal the spoils, do not be treacherous with the enemy, do not mutilate the dead, do not kill children, and fear Allah regarding the farmers who do not wage war against you.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18472,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/09\/husband-not-demand-all-rights\/","url_meta":{"origin":6637,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Marriage: Husband not demanding all his rights","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ikramah reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cI do not like to invoke all of my rights over my wife due to the saying of Allah Almighty: And for men is a degree over them.\u201d (2:228) Imam al-Tabari commented, \u201cWhat Ibn Abbas said is the 'degree,'\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/26\/ibn-abbas-no-sin-too-minor-major\/","url_meta":{"origin":6637,"position":3},"titl